    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
            The Green Schools Foundation is a dedicated group of parents, devoted alumni, educators, community leaders, and local business people.
        </p>
        <p>
            The Foundation is dedicated to furthering academic excellence in the Green Schools by providing scholarships and academic classroom grants, which benefit our elementary, middle, and high school students. Become a board member by completing and submitting the <a href="/_files/ugd/GSF%20Trustee%20Application%202024.pdf" target="_blank">trustee application</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

